Requestbody:
    will be used in post,put
    It will send the data in dict format
    Will accept only alphanumeric data .
    Won't support images or videos 
    Seperate from the url	
    usign javascript or html form we can send the requestbody
    to use class in requestbody we should use BaseModel from pydantic
    from pydantic import BaseModel


